articles.author: Shivani Naik
articles.title: Priyanshu Rajawat tries hard but can’t beat HS Prannoy, who faces Chinese leftie Weng Yang in Australian Open Super 500 final - The Indian Express
articles.description: Prannoy has played 17 three-setters this season and won 13 of those, losing only 4, but he would like to wrap up the final in two sets.
articles.content: HS Prannoy has mastered the art of finishing a set pulling out the big winners at precise moments, and proved why he is currently India’s best, downing upstart and upcoming Priyanshu Rajawat 21-18, 2… [+7420 chars]
